Product description

Reclining up to Flat position - new model IW-SK


Highly stable steel structure

Fully electrical tilting capabilities

LED / RGB lighting

IW-Skorpian King is the future of high-end home, office or gaming environments

It offers functions that enable the user to experience unprecedented comfort and total immersion through

strategically positioned monitors, audio system and accessories

The result is a complete work/gaming station which is ergonomically optimized, with minimal footprint

This improves overall performance, productivity and health and comfort

Sitting on our chair can help for relieving health problems like lower back pain, herniated discs, sciatica, neck pain and also enhance performance/viewing effects. More Luxury - More comfortable

Equipped with Luxury feeling reclining chair with thick Sponge PU leather very comfortable texture and superior quality
Reclines 128 degrees to 170 degrees for flat position

More High-End Setting - more High-tech

Manual push open/close of big sized Keyboard
Electrical control for up and down roof arms
Electrical control for reclining to flat position-including the most comfortable Zero Gravity position

More care and More healthy

Monitors distance adjustable from 23 to 32 makes a healthy & more comfortable viewing experience

More Leisure

Cup holders on the armrests for beers/coffee/ashtray etc..
Side cabinets under armrest

More Easier

Its almost fully assembled inside the shipping crate, only 1-2 hours of installation. Capacity: User: 330 lbs max. (150 kg) User Height up to 65.

Versatile Monitor Mount The IW-SK monitor mounts allows the use of a single monitor up to Ultra wide 49 or 43 in size or triple monitor setups up to 3 x 29
